{"content": "I need to multiply 258 \u00d7 703 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n258\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 162 + 45 + 8 = 215\u2081\u2080\n\n703\u2089 = 7\u00d79\u00b2 + 0\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 7\u00d781 + 0\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 567 + 0 + 3 = 570\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n215 \u00d7 570 = 215 \u00d7 (600 - 30) = 129,000 - 6,450 = 122,550\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n122550 \u00f7 9 = 13616 r 6\n13616 \u00f7 9 = 1512 r 8\n1512 \u00f7 9 = 168 r 0\n168 \u00f7 9 = 18 r 6\n18 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 0\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: 206086\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n206086\u2089 = 2\u00d759049 + 0\u00d76561 + 6\u00d7729 + 0\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 6\u00d71\n= 118098 + 0 + 4374 + 0 + 72 + 6 = 122,550\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n206086", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 441}